(Dollars milliion)      1992             1993           1993  1994
                                 Q1    Q2    Q3    Q4           Q1
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Export of goods           70     27    26    24    35    112    28
Import of goods         -575   -134  -131  -177  -179   -621  -131
