P &amp; O 5 1/2pc. Rd Non - Cum Pfd.
NEW LOWS (642).
GILTS (2) BANKS (9) ANZ, Allied Irish, Espirito Santo, HSBC HK, HSBC,
Lloyds, Natl. Australia, TSB, Westpac, BREWERIES (10) Bass, Boddington,
Fosters, Greenalls, Greene King, Marston Thompson, Paramount, Scottish &amp;
Newcastle, Vaux, Whitbread, BUILDING &amp; CNSTRN (21) BLDG MATLS &amp; MCHTS (15)
CHEMICALS (5) AGA AB, British Vita, Doeflex, Laporte, Wardle Storeys,
DISTRIBUTORS (14) DIVERSIFIED INDLS (15) ELECTRNC &amp; ELECT EQUP (18)
